hopobject.body: Special Delivery alesse birth control generics But what may be Kazakhstan's greatest strength as a candidate for the Security Council is its depth of experience in energy security. The oil and natural gas sector has attracted more than $40 billion in foreign investment to Kazakhstan since 1993, powering the economy's booming growth. But we know that traditional fossil fuels alone can't safeguard those gains, which is why Kazakh scientists, in partnership with the U.S. Department of Energy, are investigating ways to reduce the country's energy consumption, mitigate carbon emissions and develop new smart energy solutions utilizing wind, solar and other alternative sources of energy.
